          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The self-supporting C-12 targets were produced from",
                "isotopically pure powdered carbon enriched to 99.98%",
                "in C-12, the thickness was  determined using two",
                "independent method-the measurement of the contraction",
                "of the range in air of alpha particles from an",
                "americium source when the target was placed in the",
                "alpha-particle beam.The value obtained for the target",
                "to which about 90% of data are due is",
                " 13.4+-1.3 mug/cm**2 and approx. 20 mug/cm**2 for the",
                "other target. The second method used was the",
                "measurement of the excitation function over the narrow",
                "E(a)=3.6 MeV resonance-a value is 14+3 mug/cm**2 for",
                "the first target."
              ]
            }
          ],
